                                        <item name="Description" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">List of list of concrete covers [cm] of the cross section. A positive value counts from the upper cross section boundary downwards, a negative value counts from the lower cross section boundary upwards. The list of list of cover thicknesses will be mapped on the list of faces according to the longest list principle. The layers are assumed to be ordered from top (c&gt;0) to bottom (c&lt;0). Only the first four values per cross section will be considered.</item>
